                </div>
                <div class="eb-sdg-detail-intro__description">
                    <h2 class="eb-sdg-detail-intro__header">12. Responsible consumption and production</h2>
                    <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Decoupling economic growth from resource use is one of the most critical and complex challenges facing humanity today. Doing so effectively will require policies that create a conducive environment for such change, social and physical infrastructure and markets, and a profound transformation of business practices along global value chains. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Read our stories to learn more about SDG Goal 12: Responsible consumption and production</span></p>
                </div>
